CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FA dangerous driver who drank up to 10
OL,7,Fpints of beer and shots on a night out
OL,8,Fbefore he knocked down and killed a
OL,9,Fpromising law student on a pedestrian
OL,10,Fcrossing has been jailed for 12 years.
OL,12,FLiam Bowes, 37, did not stop after the
OL,13,FVW Golf he was driving struck Abigail
OL,14,FEggleston in the early hours of 26
OL,15,FOctober last year at Nevilles's Cross,
OL,16,FDurham, as he raced through red
OL,17,Ftraffic lights at 56mph when the limit
OL,18,Fwas 40mph.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
