OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FThe mechanic, from Kelloe, County
OL,7,FDurham, later tried to destroy
OL,8,Fevidence by torching the car, which he
OL,9,Fhad borrowed from a friend and for
OL,10,Fwhich he had no insurance.
OL,12,FHe was jailed at Teesside Crown Court
OL,13,Fon Monday (2 March) after admitting
OL,14,Fcausing the 22-year-old Durham
OL,15,FUniversity student's death by
OL,16,Fdangerous driving and perverting the
OL,17,Fcourse of justice by trying to burn
OL,18,Fout the car.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FHe was also sentenced for failing to
OL,7,Fstop at the scene of an accident and
OL,8,Fdriving without insurance.
OL,10,FJudge Francis Laird KC jailed him for
OL,11,F12 years, saying his wilful decision
OL,12,Fto drive while highly intoxicated
OL,13,F"resulted in the loss of a precious
OL,14,Flife".
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
