OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FDr Christopher Wood, prosecuting, said
OL,7,FBowes had been at a friend's birthday
OL,8,Fparty in Langley Park where CCTV from
OL,9,Fthe working men's club showed him
OL,10,Fdrinking "eight to 10 pints" of beer,
OL,11,Fas well as shots, with the images
OL,12,Fshowing him unsteady on his feet and
OL,13,Fbehaving erratically.
OL,15,FHe left the event around 1.30am and
OL,16,Fwas driving through Neville's Cross
OL,17,Fwhere Ms Eggleston was heading home
OL,18,Fafter a night out and was close to her
OL,19,Fstudent accommodation.
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FShe waited for the crossing light to
OL,7,Fturn green for her, despite traffic
OL,8,Fbeing light that night, and should
OL,9,Fhave been safe to cross when she was
OL,10,Fknocked down, the court heard.
OL,12,FCCTV released by Durham Constabulary
OL,13,Fshows Liam Bowes drinking at a party
OL,14,Fin Langley Park in the hours before he
OL,15,Fgot behind the wheel
OL,17,FA taxi driver waiting to turn at the
OL,18,Fjunction later told police that the VW
OL,19,FGolf driver did not brake as he went
OL,20,Fthrough the red light and hit the
OL,21,Fstudent.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
