PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FBowes did not stop at the scene,
OL,7,Fleaving her fatally injured in the
OL,8,Froad.
OL,10,FOther road-users that night stopped to
OL,11,Fhelp and blocked the road to prevent
OL,12,Fher from being further injured.
OL,14,FShe died in hospital from catastrophic
OL,15,Fhead injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
