OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FBowes was consistently driving between
OL,7,F10 and 20mph over the limit that night
OL,8,Fand covered the 14-mile journey home
OL,9,Fin under 17 minutes when it should
OL,10,Fhave taken approximately 25 minutes if
OL,11,Fhad not been speeding, Dr Wood said.
OL,13,FPolice analysed the car's on-board
OL,14,Fcomputer later and found he was going
OL,15,Fat 56mph through the lights, the court
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,18,FAfter the collision, he drove home and
OL,19,Fthen tried to set fire to the car away
OL,20,Ffrom his property.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FHe then lay low in a caravan, asking a
OL,7,Ffriend later in the day if he wanted
OL,8,Fto share a pizza as Bowes said he was
OL,9,F"starving".
OL,11,FDr Wood said Bowes was arrested and
OL,12,Fwas later to tell police he "panicked"
OL,13,Fafter the collision.
OL,15,FMandy Eggleston, Abigail's mother,
OL,16,Fsaid in a victim statement, that her
OL,17,Fdaughter had worked hard to study law
OL,18,Fand had high hopes of a successful
OL,19,Fcareer as a solicitor.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]tD@]OUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,F"Losing her has resulted in my world
OL,7,Fbeing completely and utterly crushed
OL,8,Fand destroyed, life can never be the
OL,9,Fsame again without her," the
OL,10,FNorthamptonshire mother said.
OL,12,FHer daughter was optimistic and
OL,13,Ffocused on the bright side of life,
OL,14,Fher mother said, adding: "She was
OL,15,Freally such a beautiful ray of
OL,16,Fsunshine."
OL,18,FAnd she said Bowes displayed
OL,19,F"cowardice and cruelty of the highest
OL,20,Flevel" by leaving the scene.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@XO]vD@ZOUxD@JO]{D@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/12
