PN,42510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FChristopher Morrison, defending, read
OL,7,Fout a letter from Bowes in which he
OL,8,Fsaid: "I take full responsibility for
OL,9,Fthe accident and there are no excuses
OL,10,Ffor my actions.
OL,12,F"I understand that my actions have
OL,13,Fchanged lives forever and I will
OL,14,Frightly so carry this burden with me
OL,15,Ffor the rest of my life."
OL,17,FThe court heard Bowes was the
OL,18,F"mainstay" for his mother, who has
OL,19,Fmobility problems.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUwD@YO]zD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/12
