PN,42511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772572329
OL,3,CDrunk driver jailed for 12 years after
OL,4,Ckilling law student on crossing
OL,6,FJudge Laird said Ms Eggleston was an
OL,7,F"all-rounder" who had interests in
OL,8,Fmartial arts, singing and cookery.
OL,10,FHe said: "Those who knew her have
OL,11,Fdescribed her as an intelligent, hard-
OL,12,Fworking and sensitive young woman.
OL,14,F"She was destined to do well in her
OL,15,Fstudies and had a promising and
OL,16,Ffulfilling career in law ahead of her.
OL,18,F"In short, she was full of life, she
OL,19,Fwas the daughter every parent would
OL,20,Fwant and the sister every sibling
OL,21,Fwould be fortunate to have.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]rD@JOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/12
